high_descs: Turn right into the kitchen and go to the fridge.
Take the mug off the middle shelf.
Leave the kitchen go straight ahead and take a left into the bathroom at the sink.
Put the mug in the sink and fill it with water and then take it out.
Leave the bathroom take a right and another right and go into the kitchen the second door on your left straight ahead to the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Fill a chilled Mug with water and put it in the Microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and get in the dining room, then head towards the fridge.
Open the refrigerator and pick the mug from it, then close it.
Go back to the living room and turn left, then go towards the sink.
Place the mug in the sink and wash it by opening the tap water, fetching water and closing it.
Turn around and get back to the dining room by crossing the living room with the microwave.
Then head to the corner of the room heading to microwave and place the mug in the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Fetch the water in the mug, place it in the microwave oven.

high_descs: Turn right and walk into the dining room and head to the fridge on the left.
Pick up the mug from the fridge.
Turn left and head out the dining room to walk past the diningtable and turn left to find the bathroom to reach the sink.
Fill the mug with water from the sink and pick it up.
Turn left to exit the bathroom and turn right to walk past the diningtable and walk into the dining room to reach the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the Mug full of water in the Microwave.
